ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Small Business and Tourism of JULIE CANNING of Banff, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective February 1, 2018, in the place of Rita Tsang, whose term will expire.
